\">58</sup><span class=\"wj\">As you go with your accuser before the magistrate, make an effort to settle with him on the way, lest he drag you to the judge, and the judge hand you over to the officer, and the officer put you in prison.</span></span><span class=\"v42_12_59\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.59\" class=\"v42_12_59\">59</sup><span class=\"wj\">I tell you, </span><span class=\"wj\">you will never get out until you have paid the very last </span><span class=\"wj\">penny.\u201d</span></span></p>\n</div>\n", 
